{"tid":255952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返工比人針對既感覺真係好撚慘","createTime":"2017-05-24T07:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T05:55:15.000Z","uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"429a88f2a8bab6e216e3a7dd447a8951679a899f","tid":255952,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"半年前因為上司發神經屌我<br />\n我火都黎撚埋屌返佢<br />\n之後佢同我道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後開始無窮針對之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做野做多d<br />\n特登叫其他同事孤立我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同老細開會成日吹花我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺雖然唔好受<br />\n但其他同事都知我咩事<br />\n無孤立我 <br />\n唔好在得罪左個小氣到仆街既上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住唔做<br />\n有無方法玩鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講係咪自己有問題<br />\n我唯一既問題就係屌過佢<br />\n點解屌佢因為無理取鬧<br />\n成撚日搵人發洩<br />\n屌佢老味佛都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f3cbfb3ae6e090066ec64f075b6926e3f15058","tid":255952,"uid":104618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"俾著我打鳩佢都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c96abe0ded7d41f8144a6f57d3ab5da9a6011","tid":255952,"uid":53947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"呢到冇人會話你有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a77fb130952c210945e1939d5ecc68f77dddb1","tid":255952,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"小朋友嗎???"},{"pid":"5607b775025721a942eadcf84922918423b5c863","tid":255952,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾著我打鳩佢都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文明社會"},{"pid":"525cf711e00a3dfc6a9f2c035a334aa42f8200b4","tid":255952,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"比伏佢踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030577f3835cc9eca85b4c7894bdb68dc1b5fbd7","tid":255952,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"打佢啦"},{"pid":"6f8463e4d5cad674352b33aa3d77741515d23b9a","tid":255952,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"睇佢有冇做啲不法野，同老細講"},{"pid":"78a29d5c056b7f38871edcc8ae04d32f6106c5bf","tid":255952,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"留意下佢有冇啲咩野欺上瞞下，開會爆晒比老細聽。"},{"pid":"90ce856d03686e5643971e56ab8476ea17dc8554","tid":255952,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"拎埋ref leffet玩大佢"},{"pid":"d016c6f82fdd79f9896044751b485ea3d5b49a20","tid":255952,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe76508a89ad027af596f712fb186ba72ede22d","tid":255952,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留意下佢有冇啲咩野欺上瞞下，開會爆晒比老細聽。</blockquote><br />\n成日係老細面前踩我<br />\n成日刷老細鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db78220e6908b3ea1a8d79fd3bee4ed816fd24b","tid":255952,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"佢有冇做過d唔見得光既事"}]}